  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Govanhill Roma Action</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Oxfam will be funded for one year to employ one Roma worker to support the Roma population in Govanhill to participate in the planning and delivery of the Govanhill backcourt improvement initiative. The initiative presents an opportunity to engage with the Roma population in a meaningful and inclusive way which will produce tangible outcomes for the Roma through training and employment opportunities. Whilst there will be Roma specific work and support, the approach will be to encourage and support the Roma to work alongside Govanhill community organisations, residents, health and employment groups</narrative>
  </description>
